eBook 4 Sale is a tool that will enable independent artists, writers and musicians to sell their work to the general public.  eBook 4 Sale works in two ways - by selling an electronic version of your work and/or as a marketing tool. Create a project with eBook 4 Sale, add your artwork and/or stories and music, and generate an ebook. The ebook you create can be downloaded  and sold to anyone who wishes to purchase it. This is no different than going to a book store and purchasing a printed book. The difference is that your book is "electronic" (hence "e"book) and the same people that would go to a book store can now purchase your book directly from you. Use eBook 4 Sale to make any kind of book you want, be it eComic book, ePoem book, eChildren's book, eNovel, music, or any other type of electronic book you can think of.

